---
import { education, experience } from "../data/experience";
import { site } from "../data/site";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title={`About — ${site.name}`} description={`About ${site.name}.`}>
  <h1 class="font-serif mb-10">About</h1>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <p>
      I'm a software engineer with around four years of professional experience, mostly building
      web applications in C# and JavaScript or one of its many cousins.
    </p>
    <p>
      Got into web development back when I was running a small business and got tired
      of answering the same customer questions and sharing a single Excel file with everyone
      for stock and orders. So I built something. It wasn't very good, but it got the job done. That's still how I like to approach software.
    </p>
    <p>
      Since then I've shipped production systems used by thousands of people and internal
      tools used by nobody but me. Both matter, as long as something real is getting solved.
      Although more often than I'd want to admit, what's getting solved is just my boredom.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm one of those lucky people who can make a living out of their hobby.
      And as any other hobby, it's better shared. I enjoy working through hard
      problems with other passionate people.
      Specially if they are as paranoid with format, simplicity and speed as I am :).
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
